doctype html
html
  head
    meta(charset='UTF-8')
    meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
    title Welcome to Tympact!
    style.
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px 0;
        background-color: #4f46e5;
        color: white;
        border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9fafb;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-top: none;
        border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #4f46e5;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 15px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6b7280;
      }
  body
    .header
      h1 Welcome to Tympact! ðŸŽ‰
    .content
      p Hello #{firstName},
      p Welcome to Tympact, where time is your most valuable currency! We're excited to have you on board.
      p With Tympact, you can:
      ul
        li Trade your skills and time with others
        li Earn time credits for helping others
        li Build your reputation in the community
        li Complete missions and earn rewards
      p To get started, verify your email address by clicking the button below:
      p(style='text-align: center;')
        a.button(href=url) Verify Email
      p If the button doesn't work, you can also copy and paste this link into your browser:
      p(style='word-break: break-all;') #{url}
      p If you didn't create an account with Tympact, please ignore this email.
      p Best regards,
      p The Tympact Team
    .footer
      p Â© #{new Date().getFullYear()} Tympact. All rights reserved.
      p This email was sent to #{to}. If you no longer wish to receive these emails, you can unsubscribe here.
